title: California wins Little League World Series 6-5 over Curacao on walk-off homer
description: Louis Lappe hit a walk-off homer and California beat Curacao 6-5.

title: Tropical Storm Idalia expected to become hurricane, has Florida in its sights
description: Tropical Storm Idalia is forecast to become a hurricane on Tuesday as it continues to churn off the eastern coast of Mexico's Yucatan Peninsula.

title: WATCH:  Waterspout spotted off the coast of Isle of Wight
description: A massive waterspout was spotted off the coast of the Isle of Wight in England.

title: Trump's indictment polling takeaways: Half of Americans want him to suspend campaign
description: The most recent ABC News/Ipsos poll showed problems for Trump, amid his four indictments, though he maintains his GOP primary lead in his presidential campaign

title: College student killed after accidentally trying to enter wrong house: Police
description: A University of South Carolina student was fatally shot when apparently he accidentally entered the wrong house on the street where he lived, according to police.

title: WATCH:  Over 1,000 baby river turtles released into the wild
description: A group of 1,200 baby river turtles were released back into the wild as part of a conservation project in Colombia.

title: NASCAR driver Ryan Preece is 'awake, alert and mobile' following terrifying crash
description: NASCAR driver Ryan Preece is “awake, alert and mobile” after his car rolled about a dozen times during a terrifying crash at Daytona International Speedway

title: Man killed, several injured in overnight shooting in Louisville
description: Police say an overnight shooting near a Louisville restaurant and bar has one man dead and five others injured by gunshots

title: 'Most amazing part' of GOP debate was candidates backing Trump if convicted: Christie
description: Chris Christie said the “most amazing part” of the Republican primary debate was seeing the majority of candidates say they would support Trump even if he is convicted

title: DNA confirms Wagner Group leader among crash victims, Russian officials say

title: DeSantis declares state of emergency for almost half of Florida
description: Ron DeSantis declares state of emergency in 33 Florida counties

title: Suspected killer identified in college student’s murder 36 years later
description: Cathy Sposito, a 23-year-old college student, was brutally murdered while hiking on a trail in central Arizona and authorities have now identified her suspected killer.

title: Ukraine investigates incident that killed 3 pilots while Russia attacks with cruise missiles
description: Ukrainian authorities have launched an investigation after a midair collision between two warplanes in the west of the country killed three pilots

title: 3 dead as Marine helicopter crashes in Australia during training, officials say
description: The V-22 Osprey crashed carrying about 20 service members, officials said.

title: 3 people are injured, 1 critically, in a US military aircraft crash in Australia, officials say
description: One person was in a critical condition and two others were in stable conditions.

title: North Korea to allow its citizens abroad to return home, a sign of further easing of pandemic curbs
description: North Korea says it will allow its citizens staying abroad to return home in line with easing pandemic situations worldwide

title: Firefighters douse Maui brush fire that prompted evacuations near site of deadly Lahaina blaze
description: A brush fire is prompting Maui authorities to evacuate residents.
